# Framework Architecture

The Engineering Operating Model consists of three logical layers.

```text
Governance Layer

в†“

Orchestration Layer

в†“

Execution Layer
```

## Governance Layer

Defines:

* Policies
* Standards
* Metrics
* Quality Gates
* AI Governance
* Continuous Improvement

Governance observes and improves the operating model.

---

## Orchestration Layer

Defines:

* Workflows
* Decision Flows
* Lifecycle

Workflows coordinate engineering capabilities to deliver business outcomes.

---

## Execution Layer

```text
Persona
    в†“
Capability
    в†“
Agent
    в†“
Skill
    в†“
Artifact
```

### Persona

Owns an engineering discipline.

### Capability

Represents reusable engineering functions.

### Agent

Human or AI executor.

### Skill

Reusable engineering procedure.

### Artifact

Output produced by a skill.

